learnings: Team talk triggers were using legacy agent names from pre-JaiOS 4.0 era
Inter-AI messages had no acknowledgment protocol causing dropped handovers
Meetings directory was never created despite being referenced in boardroom protocol
Feedback engine itself was never being called by any agent workflow
